'''Oxonmoot 2017''', the 44th annual [[Oxonmoot]] hosted by [[The Tolkien Society]], took place [[21 September|21]]-[[24 September]] at St Antony's College, [[University of Oxford|Oxford]]. The event included a performance of ''[[Leaf by Niggle]]''.
